## Image Upload Screens

If screen includes avatar/homebrew image → `docs/05_FRONTEND_SPEC.md` Bölüm 11 (presigned URL, client resize, no SVG).

## Error and Not Found

| HTTP | UI behavior |
| --- | --- |
| 404 | `NotFoundPage` or inline "not found" |
| 403 | Toast: API `message`; redirect if DM-only |
| 401 | Auth slice clear → `/login` |

Global error boundary for 500 → Faz 5 (`docs/06` Grup 8).

## Performance Notes

- RTK Query `skip: !id` when param undefined.
- List pages: virtualize only if catalog requires (post-MVP default: pagination).
- Lazy-load heavy builder steps if character builder (`docs/05` Bölüm 14).

## Troubleshooting

| Problem | Fix |
| --- | --- |
| Infinite redirect login | `isLoading` guard before Navigate |
| Stale list after mutation | `invalidatesTags` / `providesTags` |
| CORS on API | Bearer via RTK `prepareHeaders`, not cookie for access |
| Turkish validation | Zod messages in shared schema — English only |

